                                            <div class="mt-16">
                        <strong class="font-bold uppercase">The Project</strong><p>A pitch where Suzuki wanted a concept of an interactive idea to promote their new model. The client’s only optional preference was to have the car spin 360 degrees</p><strong class="font-bold uppercase"></strong>My Role</strong><p>I was responsible for the concept, idea and implementation</p><strong class="font-bold uppercase"></strong>The Result</strong><p>As just rotating the car do not give the user much value, I came up with an interactive idea where the spin effect became an informative and fact-based idea, based on the car’s special features for each season</p><p>NOTE: This showcase an idea rather than final artwork</p> 
